'''Alderaan Biotics''' was an [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]]-based [[Hydroponics/Legends|hydroponics]] company. Their [[Borleias/Legends|Borleias]] satellite [[Alderaan Biotics facility|facility]], abandoned before the destruction of Alderaan due to lack of profit, was eventually reactivated by [[Evir Derricote]] and later co-opted by the forces of [[Ysanne Isard]] prior to the [[Bacta War]]. [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] would soon recapture the facility. Through the Borleias facility, Alderaan Biotics would go on to become a large manufacturer of [[rylca]].

